After three individual sessions, the foursomes on Saturday afternoon may be just what this Ryder Cup needed.
The pendulum swing is a completely invented concept in sports, but the players really believe in it, even more so in competitions like these.
Then, where would they say the impulse is now?
“We were six points behind and now we’re four points behind, so I guess you could say that’s a little bit of a push,” said Jordan Spieth after the round.
